Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:34.43,Copy of Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,"Operation: Infiltrate a Planetoid Base"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fast! I can't process\Ntheir data quick enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My unit feels heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it get fat?! Did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is gravity since we're on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I can't keep up with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, get your acts together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your controls will go \Nbonkers if you panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Team Rabbits?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly their AHSMB \Nunits are under repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're still considered students,\Nthey're getting a supplementary lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just me, or do they \Nsuck even worse now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're the other three?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Students can't pull \Noff moves like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining Miracle Turn Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I put my faith in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll charge ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their formation is a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that Miracle-whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My secret move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, figures. Most heroes\Nhave a secret move, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But heroes use secret \Nmoves to save the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure I could pull it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all we needed was confidence,\Nwe'd get 100's studying by ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never got to show my stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't looking too \Nhot out there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freakin' out after \Nthat string of losses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your training session is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Rabbits, everyone \Nis to submit your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,own personal analysis on why you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble in the Meeting Room in 30 minutes\Nwith Team Doberman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirs, thank you for the lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Team Doberman for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't they also students here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly they were \Nhighly accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A joint meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we're working with them\Non our next mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be super awesome!\NAll three dudes are stud muffins!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you can act so carefree
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nafter nearly getting killed in that last mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear and romance are \Ntwo different things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the Fail Five are\Nstill the Fail Five, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come they get to pilot\Ncutting-edge fighters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My entrance may come \Nsurprisingly soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my Likeability Stats would go up\Nafter becoming a wee bit famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame them \Nfor feeling that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get down to it,\Nour team only won that very first battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're blasting us on \Nthe internet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring that up.\NYou'll give me another ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your AHSMB units have \Nbeen fully repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be transferring \Nto Star Rose tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon arrival, we will \Ncommence a co-op mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, what if we fail again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking like that will only hinder\Nyour performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time you've got \NTeam Doberman with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Commander, I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been meaning to \Nask this for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me your personal address\Nand when you're off duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Randy, we're in the middle of a meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't ask such \Nshameless questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya don't ask stuff \Nlike this when you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nyou could forever miss the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you as our clown of a leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people keep calling \Nus the "Bummer Three,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe "Comedic Three" and "Trio Dobermans."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Bummer Three"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect from our seniors!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being \Nthe Bummer Three?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do you always act\Nlike you're better than me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because we're classmates\Ndoesn't mean you can walk all over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sub-leader's job to guide\Nthe leader down the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, the \Ndisciplinary committee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.93,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pardon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.48,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why must you always act so cool?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.46,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you going on about\Nin the middle of a meeting?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.12,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you think you're on \Nthe Cool Committee?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't have time to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.54,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should try to act a \Nbit more like a leader!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are no further questions,\Nthis meeting is adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. My team \Nalways acts like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit acting like you're \Nexcluded from our antics!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, that hurts! Randy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.18,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up! Uncle, uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God they aren't \Nas scary as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.08,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? I couldn't hear you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, they're funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.72,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're still cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they saved our hides!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're totally the hero type!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll really let you have it next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, you never change!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Thank you\Nfor saving me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, aren't you Red 5's pilot...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Izuru Hitachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like ages \Nsince I was here last.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it rough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sending you out hunting\Nwhen you're still just a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are gonna say what they're gonna say;\Ndon't worry 'bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I get sent to battle,\NI wonder if I'm doing enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've survived this far!\NIsn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to become a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Why do you want to \Nbe a hero of all things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I think they're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what it takes\Nto be a hero. You must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...good looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, it's all about the looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a hero, you gotta \Nbe the best looking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nmember in your group and get all of the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I a prime example?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the record, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you aren't as handsome as me,\Nbut you're plenty good looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you'll \Nbecome an amazing hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is-is that right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, what else is there...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose you could say\Nthat a hero has three jobs:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making decisions, never giving up\Nand believing in your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you trust them... your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched the footage from all of\NTeam Rabbits' battles so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You try to do everything yourself while
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ndesperately fighting to protect your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't keep a team together\Nif you don't believe in your men!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now putting that aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pilots for Unit 2 and Unit 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you have your sights set on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:09:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they both adorable? \NWhich is your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you already dating one of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I couldn't possibly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a team, so that \Nsort of stuff is taboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe my ears!\NJust how old are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, Suruga and I are 16.\NAsagi is 17. Tamaki is 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the best days of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta fall in love,\Nsquabble and then break up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Swap teams with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, you're Team Doberman's leader;\NI'm taking Rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm just pulling your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes looked kinda serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our line of work, you never know\Nwhen you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you like someone to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwho you were after you're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interact with as many people\Nas you possibly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure you remember\Neach person you meet along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Study this with the pilots \Nfor Unit 1 and Unit 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it contain footage \Nfrom our battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this and put your \Nbest foot forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Does it \Ncontain video records?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! He said to only watch it\Nwith Asagi and Suruga,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I figured we could \Nall watch it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn't exactly \Nwhat I was expecting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pro wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what? What?\NWh-what's the big deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bit much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you freaking out when you're\Nthe one constantly flirting with the ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-but this is on a totally \Ndifferent level...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! If we get caught,\Nreports will be the least of our worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't mean-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! This is truly ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This actress resembles \NInstructor Suzukaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention \Nit, I can see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission's name is \NOperation: MacLean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are to infiltrate the enemy base on\NPlanetoid RA221 and blow it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, what do you think \Nhas gotten into them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what to \Nexpect once you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it isn't terribly big,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we believe the base's\Nartificial gravity device is active.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have outfitted your units\Nfor fighting in gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was our training on \NEarth before the mission
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nmeant to serve as a simulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is far enough away from the battlefield\Nthat we expect minimal security.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, with weak transmission signals,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nit will be impossible to communicate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold 4 will be in charge of the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will also use Gold 4's\Ncomputer to detonate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mission came out \Nof nowhere, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we're destroying\Na base that's on the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably trying to make\Nthe other team look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it'd take \Nto save the MJP's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, they want evidence\Nthat we're winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this is a co-op to increase\Nthe chances of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but do you think \Nwe can handle this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you end up watching \Nthat video last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me! I didn't watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, are you going to \Ntell the instructor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-don't worry, Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy after staying up all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was really refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Was it a good picker upper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I wound up showing it\Nto Kei and Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Y-you've got some balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you've treaded grounds\Nfar more dangerous than I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-gee, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Identifying the enemy base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm forwarding the image.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we expecting minimal security?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?\NWithdraw and request new orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't reach our commanding officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to make the \Ncall for ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's carry out the mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the base is crowded with enemies\Nwhen it shouldn't be,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it means they're up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go back empty-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! They found us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how? Do they have eyes and ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My team will draw the enemy fire
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhile your team carries out the mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will you be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a gravity reactor\Nat the center of the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set the bomb there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do fine as long \Nas you remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want us to infiltrate\Nthe base by ourselves...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet absolutely refuse to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your willpower to rein in the\NJURIA-SYSTEM's survival instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:14:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Red 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me, Purple 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do if they find us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doberman is attracting all\Nof the enemy's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine... I think... maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the base's guards\Nstill don't know we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we could get in through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose 3 can't fit through that entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Izuru?\NLeave Tamaki behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make up your mind before \Nthe gate closes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll probably need to shoot down\Nany enemy fighters that come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We can handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, Suruga, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a Wulgaru base...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm detecting a reactor located\N250 meters below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we blow that up, it should\Ntake out the entire base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the route?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy fighters incoming at 2:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suruga, protect the bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, can you activate \Nthe defense shields?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could, but they'll make scanning\Nand analyzing the area that much harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Then we'll plow \Nthrough without them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing we trained on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the upcoming 90° \Nturn to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next drop 90° vertically down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat values are higher\Nthan I had anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sudden fluctuation in heat is beginning\Nto interfere with my sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you at least tell \Nwhat direction it's in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow the artificial gravity pipeline,\Nwe should reach the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean we're gonna keep\Nfalling for who knows how long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't holding back even though\Nwe're inside their base!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a given!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we destroy this reactor,\Nit'll send the whole base sky high!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got hit somewhere along the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I can't set it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission's a failure! \NWe gotta retreat. Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Izuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suruga, can you fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's beyond me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't make it back alive\Nif we don't destroy this base.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our only option if \Nwe hope to survive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suruga, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, use your shields to protect Suruga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll distract the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! I guess this is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to survive... Everyone is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if everyone's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll come back safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise my stomach will kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Suruga! Izuru is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all set! I'm a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Now let's withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secondary explosions \Nare going off fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get caught in the \Nblast if we don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! What type of \Nenergy are they using?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't make it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly accelerated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instinct to survive \Nmeans serious business!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you three are lost without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so sure I was \Ngonna die this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lookin' good there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero of the Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:55.99,Copy of Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,"Graduation"
